dict.string: HandBrake's settings for compatibility with all Apple devices (including the iPod 6G and later). Includes Dolby Digital audio for surround sound.
HandBrake's settings for playback on the iPod with Video (all generations).
HandBrake's settings for handheld iOS devices (iPhone 4, iPod touch 3G and later).
HandBrake's settings for playback on the iPad (all generations).
HandBrake's settings for the original AppleTV. Includes Dolby Digital audio for surround sound. Also compatible with iOS devices released since 2009.
HandBrake's settings for the second-generation AppleTV. Includes Dolby Digital audio for surround sound. NOT compatible with the original AppleTV.
HandBrake's settings for the third-generation AppleTV. Includes Dolby Digital audio for surround sound. NOT compatible with the original AppleTV. May stutter on the second-generation AppleTV.
HandBrake's settings for midrange devices running Android 2.3 or later.
HandBrake's preset for tablets running Android 2.3 or later.
